---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<Layout title="Agita - Joel Huggett" description="A terminal UI for streamlining Git workflows.">
  <PageHeader title="" />
  <main class="post-wrapper">
    <article>
      <a href="/apps" class="post-back">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M9.4 233.4c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l160 160c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0s12.5-32.8 0-45.3L109.2 288 416 288c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32l-306.7 0L214.6 118.6c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0l-160 160z"/></svg>
        Apps
      </a>
      <h1 class="post-title">Agita</h1>

      <p class="game-tagline">Git TUI</p>

      <div class="game-video-wrapper">
        <video src="/agita-vid.mov" autoplay loop controls playsinline muted></video>
      </div>

      <p class="paragraph">
        Instead of continually typing the same git commands over and over again — and then re-typing them because of a typo — just select the command from a text-based user interface.
      </p>

      <p class="paragraph">
        Agita is a terminal UI that streamlines your Git workflow. Run <code>agita</code> in any directory containing a Git repository to get a selection-based interface for common operations: status, staging, committing, pushing, pulling, and branch management.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin: 2rem 1rem 0.5rem;">Install</h2>
      <pre class="app-install-cmd"><code>npm install -g agita</code></pre>

      <ul class="tags-list" style="margin: 1rem;">
        <li class="tag">Node.js</li>
        <li class="tag">CLI</li>
        <li class="tag">Git</li>
        <li class="tag">TUI</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="game-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/jhuggett/agita" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="game-link">
          <svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405 1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/></svg>
          Source Code
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/agita" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="game-link">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 576 512"><path d="M288 288h-32v-64h32v64zm288-128v192H288v32H160v-32H0V160h576zm-416 32H32v128h64v-96h32v96h32V192zm160 0H192v160h64v-32h64V192zm224 0H352v128h64v-96h32v96h32v-96h32v96h32V192z"/></svg>
          npm
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
